title: Egypt northern Sinai bomb kills first lieutenant, 2 soldiers
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer - Today 
An Egyptian first lieutenant and two soldiers were killed in an explosion which targeted a police armored vehicle in the northern Sinai city...
